OL,4,CRape victims: Calls for pre-recorded
OL,5,Cevidence to be used in trials
OL,6, Rape victims in England and Wales
OL,7, should be able to pre-record evidence
OL,8, and cross-examinations so that they do
OL,9, not have to face perpetrators in court,
OL,10, the victims' commissioner has said.
OL,12,FIn a new report, Dame Vera Baird has
OL,13,Fcalled for the practice to be rolled
OL,14,Fout "as soon as practically possible".
OL,16,FIt would also reduce stressful waits in
OL,17,Fthe run-up to trials, she told the BBC.
OL,19,FThe BBC understands the government is
OL,20,Fconsidering the move, but it is not
OL,21,Fclear how it would be implemented.
